Name: The Amazing Race Canada
Title: Where Are You Mr. Oyster
Desc: Racers make waves on the East Coast and try to zip through the competition in Miramichi, NB.
LongDescription: Racers make waves on the East Coast and try to zip through the competition in Miramichi, New Brunswick; the heat is on as the remaining teams try to earn their way into a coveted spot on the season ten finale.
